# 📞 Phone Validation API

**Enterprise-grade phone number validation. 60% cheaper than Twilio.**

[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-blue.svg)](LICENSE)
[![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.11+-blue.svg)](https://python.org)
[![FastAPI](https://img.shields.io/badge/FastAPI-0.104-green.svg)](https://fastapi.tiangolo.com)
[![Deployed on Render](https://img.shields.io/badge/deployed-Render-purple.svg)](https://render.com)

---

## 🚀 What This API Does

Validate phone numbers from **200+ countries** in real-time. Get carrier, timezone, and location data — all at **60% less cost** than Twilio.

| Feature | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| ✅ Real-time validation | Check if a phone number exists and is reachable |
| 📡 Carrier detection | Identify mobile carrier (AT&T, Kyivstar, Vodafone, etc.) |
| 🌍 Location data | Country, city, and region information |
| ⏰ Timezone detection | IANA timezone (e.g., America/Los_Angeles, Europe/Kyiv) |
| 📦 Batch processing | Validate up to 100 numbers in one request |
| 📁 Bulk CSV upload | Upload thousands of numbers via CSV file |
| 🔗 Webhooks | Get notified when invalid numbers are detected |
| 📊 Usage dashboard | Track your API usage and remaining limits |
| 🔒 GDPR compliant | No data storage, fully compliant |

